{"title":"心中的国度","authors":["妮脂　白开元"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中的国度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔孟加拉国〕妮脂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撩拨我的心弦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇撼我的灵府；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯洁的心幕上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮现着日新月异的版图："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心目中的国度——中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向科学、文化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和经济发展的顶峰攀登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜蜜生活的美好景象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十亿人民希望的乐园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将成为人类文明的光辉象征。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心目中的国度——中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如花香招来蜜蜂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如美女迷醉恋人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以奇迹将我吸引。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天，今天，明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远让我看到前进的方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓舞我奔赴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充满欢笑的光辉灿烂的未来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心目中的国度——中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白开元译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}